Narrator: BEDTIME AT
THE LONGBOROUGH SCHOOL FOR BOYS

00:46.698 --> 00:49.614
WAS A TIME FOR DREAMS --

00:49.658 --> 00:51.616
DREAMS FILLED WITH THE BLISS

00:51.660 --> 00:54.141
THAT CAME
FROM A HAPPY CHILDHOOD.

00:57.187 --> 00:58.623
BUT ON THIS NIGHT,

00:58.667 --> 01:01.757
ONE BOY CHOSE TO DREAM
WITH HIS EYES WIDE OPEN.

01:01.800 --> 01:04.934
11 WEEKS, 1 DAY, 7 HOURS,
AND 41 MINUTES AGO,

01:04.977 --> 01:07.806
YOUNG NED WAS LIVING
THAT HAPPY CHILDHOOD,

01:07.850 --> 01:10.461
COMPLETE WITH A LOVELY HOME,
CARING MOTHER,

01:10.505 --> 01:13.986
AND BOYHOOD SWEETHEART --
A GIRL HE CALLED CHUCK.

01:14.030 --> 01:16.076
BUT WHEN HIS MOTHER DIED, TWICE,

01:16.119 --> 01:18.730
YOUNG NED AWOKE
TO A NEW REALITY.

01:18.774 --> 01:20.950
THOUGH HE COULD
REANIMATE THE DEAD,

01:20.993 --> 01:23.300
YOUNG NED COULD ONLY ANIMATE
THE INANIMATE

01:23.344 --> 01:26.651
WITH HIS IMAGINATION.

01:26.695 --> 01:30.916
ON THIS LONELY NIGHT, HE TRIED
TO RE-CREATE HIS PAST LIFE.

01:34.398 --> 01:36.661
BUT HE'D LOST
HIS ABILITY TO DREAM

01:36.705 --> 01:39.447
AND FOUND EVEN HIS IMAGINATION
FAILED HIM.

01:39.490 --> 01:41.275
[ WHIMPERS ]

01:48.499 --> 01:51.981
STILL, HE WORE HOPE ON HIS HEAD.

01:54.244 --> 01:57.987
AND WHAT YOUNG NED DIDN'T KNOW
WAS AT THAT VERY MOMENT,

01:58.030 --> 02:03.253
THE GIRL HE CALLED CHUCK
WAS WEARING HOPE ON HERS.

02:03.297 --> 02:09.041
THEY WERE TOGETHER,
EVEN IF THEY WERE FAR APART.

02:09.085 --> 02:11.653
LITTLE DID THEY KNOW
THAT WHEN THEY WOULD AWAKE

02:11.696 --> 02:17.049
19 YEARS, 51 WEEKS, 2 DAYS,
9 HOURS, AND 13 MINUTES LATER,

02:17.093 --> 02:21.706
THEY WOULD AGAIN BE TOGETHER,
YET STILL SO FAR APART.

02:21.750 --> 02:25.971
FOR UNFORTUNATELY, THE PIE MAKER
COULD NEVER, EVER TOUCH HER.

02:26.015 --> 02:27.669
